{"tid":1383093,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"平價闊視野泳鏡， 大家同我清左佢！","createTime":"2019-07-29T15:28:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T16:12:47.000Z","uid":14953,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"98c1726db629f2c679ca4629f8affa59c5407680","tid":1383093,"uid":14953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:28:32.000Z","msg":"我都係自己買完先敢放上黎。話說迪卡儂一直有款唔貴既泳鏡一直冇貨。但我早兩日留意到佢倉返左貨。 $89一副重要泳鏡係一定氣密，留返鼻位又唔會用唔到口罩。未真正試過但相信視野開揚。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2iki3QX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2iki3QX.png&h=f98a08af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相反我買左3M 2980s/ 2980sa 果d 鼻位反而封唔晒， 唔加口罩就會漏氣。<br />\n<br />\n補返條link<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.decathlon.com.hk/en/p/100-swimdow-asia-swim-mask-size-l-blue-yellow/_/R-p-148703\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.decathlon.com.hk%2Fen%2Fp%2F100-swimdow-asia-swim-mask-size-l-blue-yellow%2F_%2FR-p-148703&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJZuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=4c60296e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.decathlon.com.hk/en/p/100-swimdow-asia-swim-mask-size-l-blue-yellow/_/R-p-148703</a>"},{"pid":"ae6bd2ff16c91177b3da5df5d49f69f95f64136f","tid":1383093,"uid":235580,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:37:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t4Dpe1t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft4Dpe1t.jpg&h=8a64558c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nUvex Ultravision Gas Goggle<br />\n<br />\n呢隻夠貼面夠密封<br />\n<br />\nComfortable gas-tight goggle<br />\nContact Heat resistant, flame retardant body<br />\n180&deg; field of vision<br />\nSupravision anti-scratch, anti-fog lens<br />\nEN 166 1B 3459 KN<br />\nEN 170<br />\n<br />\nCarousell 有人賣 $40， made in Germany, 抵到爛<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.carousell.com/p/uvex-%E9%98%B2%E8%AD%B7%E7%9C%BC%E7%BD%A9-%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E5%88%B6-196061131/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.carousell.com%2Fp%